FT  26 FEB 93 / UK Company News: Reshaped Dunkeld in black
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
DUNKELD Group, the clothing manufacturer which recently completed a
financial restructuring, turned in a pre-tax profit of Pounds 2.45m for the
year to November 30.
That compared with a deficit of Pounds 17.5m last time and was struck on
