and included some Pounds 10m of restructuring costs.
At the operating level, profits amounted to Pounds 1.24m (Pounds 4.43m
losses), of which continuing operations contributed Pounds 1.53m from
turnover of Pounds 17m.
The reconstructed group now has two trading divisions, shirts and swimwear,
both of which traded profitably in 1992.
Earnings per share came out at 3.16p (29.21p losses).
