Domestic fuel and power                             pounds2.6bn
Domestic fares                                      pounds1.1bn
International fares                                 pounds0.8bn
Books, newspapers etc                               pounds1.1bn
Children's clothing                                 pounds0.6bn
Water/sewerage services                             pounds0.7bn
Medicines                                           pounds0.5bn
Supplies to charities                               pounds0.2bn
Some ships, aircraft                                pounds0.5bn
Rent*                                               pounds2.3bn
