   By HILARY BARNES
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   COPENHAGEN
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Impeachment proceedings are being prepared by the Danish parliament against
a former minister of justice, Mr Erik Ninn-Hansen, for his part in the visa
scandal which brought down the Conservative-Liberal coalition government
last month, writes Hilary Barnes in Copenhagen. Mr Ninn-Hansen, as minister
