<TEXT>
MR Brice Lalonde, head of Generation Ecologie, one of France's leading
environmental movements, has endorsed the proposal by Mr Michel Rocard, the
former French prime minister, for an alliance between socialists and
ecologists, writes Alice Rawsthorn in Paris.
Mr Lalonde, who resigned last year as environment minister, said the
