Mr Lalonde's endorsement is a step forward for Mr Rocard, who needs to
secure the ecologists' support for his proposal. Leading figures on the left
have backed Mr Rocard, including Mr Pierre Beregovoy, prime minister, and Mr
Bernard Kouchner, the popular health minister.
