FT  25 FEB 93 / UK Company News: Jos Holdings show improvement
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Jos Holdings, which last year became a split capital investment trust after
a reorganisation, raised net profits from Pounds 186,000 to Pounds 287,000
in the six months to January 31 1993.
